INSERT INTO projects (slug, title, subtitle, category, image, description, challenge, solution, results, technologies, downloadUrl, published) VALUES (
  'fortune-500-innovation',
  'Fortune 500 Innovation Architecture',
  'Enterprise 0-1 Solutions',
  'Enterprise',
  '/images/project-cloud-migration.png',
  'Coordinated cross-functional teams across product, engineering, and business groups for 4 Fortune 500 clients at Wilde Group, using research and design thinking workshops to define 0-1 solution opportunities that shaped early architecture direction.',
  'Translate research findings into prioritized technical focus areas while evaluating system constraints and technology gaps across multiple Fortune 500 enterprise environments. Needed to guide early architecture exploration and improve cross-team alignment during development planning.',
  'Guided early architecture exploration by translating research findings into prioritized technical focus areas. Partnered with engineering leads to evaluate system constraints and technology gaps, producing modernization recommendations. Provided data-informed inputs to R&D-style planning efforts, strengthening C-suite clarity on technology priorities.',
  JSON_ARRAY('Contributed to launch of 9 enterprise innovation initiatives', 'Reduced integration blockers by 25% across 3 business units', 'Cut early-stage architectural alignment cycles by 30%', 'Improved cross-team alignment during 0-N development planning'),
  JSON_ARRAY('Enterprise Architecture', 'Cloud Migration', 'API Integration', 'Design Thinking', 'System Modernization'),
  '/documents/enterprise-architecture.pdf',
  true
);
